---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const schema = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "AboutPage",
  "name": "About Mind Success Program",
  "url": "https://mindsuccessprogram.com/about/",
  "description": "Learn about Mind Success Program — our mission, values, and commitment to helping you achieve extraordinary success through mindset transformation."
};
---

<Layout
  title="About Us — Mind Success Program"
  description="Our mission is to help you unlock your full potential through the world's best mindset programs, expert reviews, and evidence-based personal development resources."
  schema={schema}
>
  <section class="py-20 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <p class="text-[#D4AF37] font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3 text-sm">Our Story</p>
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-black text-white mb-4" style="font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;">About Mind Success Program</h1>
    </div>

    <!-- Affiliate Disclosure -->
    <div class="card-bg rounded-xl p-4 border border-[#D4AF37]/20 mb-10 flex items-start gap-3">
      <span class="text-[#D4AF37] text-xl mt-0.5">ℹ️</span>
      <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">
        <strong class="text-gray-300">Affiliate Disclosure:</strong> Mind Success Program participates in affiliate marketing programs including Mindvalley, NeuroGym, Amazon Associates, Blinkist, and Audible. We earn a commission when you purchase through our links, at no extra cost to you. We only recommend products and services we genuinely believe in.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="prose-dark">
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        Mind Success Program was born from a simple but powerful realization: <strong class="text-white">the quality of your life is determined by the quality of your mind.</strong> Everything you achieve — or fail to achieve — flows from the beliefs, habits, and mental frameworks running in the background of your consciousness.
      </p>

      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>To cut through the noise of the personal development industry and connect you with the programs, tools, and techniques that actually work. We believe that extraordinary success is available to anyone willing to do the inner work — and our job is to make that work as clear, accessible, and effective as possible.</p>

      <h2>What Makes Us Different</h2>
      <p>There are thousands of personal development websites. Most of them regurgitate the same generic advice, promote whatever product pays the highest commission, and never actually test the programs they recommend.</p>
      <p>We do things differently:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>We test everything we review.</strong> Every program we recommend has been personally used by our team for at least 30 days. We don't write reviews from press releases or marketing materials.</li>
        <li><strong>We prioritize science over hype.</strong> When a program claims to be "neuroscience-based," we actually check the research. When a technique is recommended, we explain the mechanism behind why it works.</li>
        <li><strong>We're honest about what doesn't work.</strong> We call out overhyped products, misleading claims, and programs that don't deliver. Your trust is more valuable than any affiliate commission.</li>
        <li><strong>We give away our best content for free.</strong> Our pillar guides, blog articles, and resources are comprehensive, actionable, and completely free. We only earn when we genuinely help you find the right paid program for your goals.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Our Values</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Integrity First:</strong> We will never recommend a product we don't believe in, regardless of commission rates.</li>
        <li><strong>Evidence Over Opinion:</strong> Our recommendations are grounded in research, not personal preference or marketing hype.</li>
        <li><strong>Radical Honesty:</strong> We tell you the downsides, not just the upsides. Every review includes what could be better.</li>
        <li><strong>Your Success Is Our Success:</strong> We measure our impact by the transformations our readers achieve, not by page views or revenue.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How We Make Money</h2>
      <p>We're transparent about our business model. Mind Success Program generates revenue through affiliate partnerships with the programs we review. When you click a link and make a purchase, we may earn a commission at no extra cost to you.</p>
      <p>This model allows us to provide comprehensive free content while keeping the lights on. But it comes with a critical commitment: <strong class="text-white">we only partner with programs we genuinely believe in and have personally tested.</strong> If a program doesn't meet our standards, we don't promote it — regardless of how much it pays.</p>

      <h2>Our Process</h2>
      <p>Every review and guide on this site follows a rigorous process:</p>
      <ol>
        <li><strong>Research:</strong> We study the program's methodology, instructor credentials, and any available research supporting its claims.</li>
        <li><strong>Testing:</strong> Our team personally uses the program for a minimum of 30 days, following the protocols as designed.</li>
        <li><strong>Analysis:</strong> We evaluate the program across six dimensions: content quality, instructor credibility, scientific foundation, platform experience, community support, and value for money.</li>
        <li><strong>Writing:</strong> We produce comprehensive, honest reviews that include both strengths and weaknesses.</li>
        <li><strong>Updating:</strong> We revisit our reviews regularly as programs evolve and new information becomes available.</li>
      </ol>

      <h2>Join the Community</h2>
      <p>Whether you're just beginning your personal development journey or you're a seasoned practitioner looking for the next level, you're in the right place. Explore our <a href="/mindset-training/" class="text-[#D4AF37] hover:underline">mindset training guide</a>, read our <a href="/reviews/" class="text-[#D4AF37] hover:underline">program reviews</a>, or dive into our <a href="/blog/" class="text-[#D4AF37] hover:underline">latest articles</a>.</p>
      <p>Your extraordinary life is waiting. Let's build it together.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
